setMenuOptions

public void setMenuOptions(String[] menuOptions)
Sets this card's contextual menu options. A card must be subscribed to receive events from the Toq smartwatch to trigger contextual menu events in the DeckOfCardsEventListener. An individual menu option may not be null or a zero length String; any whitespace will be trimmed.
